  "abstract": "Sweet sorghum (Sorghum bicolor (L.) Moench) is one of the promising feedstock for\r\nbioethanol production worldwide. It is a food-feed-fuel-industrial crop, which requires low water\r\nand fertilizer input, has moderate grain yield and high yield of biomass for bio-refining and\r\nindustrial utilization......",
